open feign
feign is a declarative web service-client designed to make writing HTTP clients easier
so as of now to communicate between two microservices we are using RestTemplate
for this resttemplate we need to write boilerplate again and again

for example below code
Company company = restTemplate.getForObject("http://COMPANYMS/companies/"+job.getCompanyId(),Company.class);

will be converted to
Company company = companyClient.getCompany(job.getCompanyId());

Feign internally uses Ribbon to provide client-side load balancing and service discovery